    "title": "ICICI Prudential Life is Hiring: Credit Analyst (Senior)",
    "description": "Grow your career with ICICI Prudential Life! We are hiring a Credit Analyst for our Delhi team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout ICICI Prudential Life:\nICICI Prudential Life is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with ICICI Prudential Life!",
